 1483                   
 1484                   ; Read one sector from disk.
 1485                   ; Return a 00h in A if the operation completes properly, and 01h if an error occurs during the read.
 1486                   ; Disk number in 'diskno' (4..7)
 1487                   ; Track number in 'track' (0..255)
 1488                   ; Sector number in 'sector' (0..63)
 1489                   ; DMA address in 'dmaad' (0-65535)
 1490                   ; 
 1491                   ; LBA
 1492                   ; 00000000 00000000 00000000
 1493                   ; 00000000 tttttttt ssssssdd
 1494                   ;        E        B        C
